@DATABASE "Blade Warrior"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - B - Blade Warrior"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - B
                   ====================================

                               Blade Warrior
                               =============


DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(37161,0)"}          37161,0
@{"Infinite Time " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(37161,151)"}          37161,151

                         These POKEs are "mutually exclusive" (It says here).
                         What this means you can only have one or the other,
                         not both (they POKE the same address y'see)
                                                                     Rastan
